                  2026 is properly recorded in the checklist.<br>
                  <br>
                </b><br>
                <b>The problem — and it is a process problem, not a
                  content problem</b><br>
                <br>
                I have reviewed both the FSD Document Identity table and
                the Review Checklist document carefully.<b> There are
                  two specific issues.</b><br>
                <br>
                <b>First:</b> the TL-IST sign-off. The FSD Document
                Identity table reads: 'SIGNED OFF. TL IST: PENDING.'
                That is a contradiction in one sentence. It cannot be
                both signed off and pending. More importantly, I have
                checked the Review Checklist document you attached. The
                Stage 3 TL-IST section shows every tick box as empty and
                the Stage 3 sign-off box is completely blank — no name
                and no date. There is no evidence in either document
                that Palanivel has performed the TL-IST review.<br>
