                field experience from 14 years in IT and 10+ years at
                Kalpatharu. His specific task is to independently verify
                each of Muthuvel's IST answers from his own customer
                site experience — not to read Muthuvel's answers and
                agree, but to confirm or correct them from his own
                knowledge. The Stage 3 checklist items include: IST-2
                approval screen URL independently confirmed, IST-4
                support patterns verified with additions from own senior
                experience, and independent commentary added as a
                separate column in the review.<br>
                <br>
                <b>This is domain work that only Palanivel can do. </b>Your
                Stage 4 review verifies completeness and build-readiness
                — that is a different kind of review and does not
                substitute for the domain validation that Stage 3
                requires. The process chain was designed this way
                deliberately. <b>Collapsing two stages into one
                  undermines the quality gate the chain is intended to
                  provide.<br>
                </b><br>
